Peru Ready to Lift Liquidity if World Growth Slows, Velarde Says

-- B y   J o h n   Q u i g l e y
-- 
2011-09-21T18:57:43Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-21/peru-ready-to-lift-liquidity-if-world-growth-slows-velarde-says.html
Peru ’s central bank is ready to
increase liquidity in the nation’s financial system if global
markets deteriorate, the bank’s president Julio Velarde said.  There are no signs of a deceleration in the Peruvian
economy yet, Velarde said today during a news conference at  New
York ’s Princeton Club.  To contact the reporter on this story:
